item.content:encoded:
Fishing Master is a relaxing simulation game. After choosing the target fish, you can start clicking the water till you catch the fish. The fish will try to get rid of you and escape in a few seconds. When you earn some cash, I recommend you upgrade your strength first. The next fish will always be stronger than the last one.
On PC and MobileKeep tapping on the screen
